-- South Africa Rescue Workers Free 4 Trapped Miners
-- B y   H i l t o n   S h o n e
-- 2013-11-25T13:30:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-25/south-africa-rescue-workers-free-4-trapped-miners.html
Paramedics free men trapped at old
mine near Robertville, west of Johannesburg, ER24 emergency
service says in e-mailed statement.
*Men went missing 3 days ago
*4 men thought to be illegal miners; taken into custody  To contact the reporter on this story:
